## How you'll be assessed at service assessments

    To meet the Service Standard, you'll need to demonstrate at service assessments how you have tested your service so it works for everyone.

    ### Discovery

    - consider the assisted technology routes to the service, for example, people using <a href="https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/technology/testing-with-assistive-technologies" target="_blank" rel="noopner noreferrer">screen readers, speech recognition software and magnifiers (opens in new tab)</a>.
    - research with users with access needs and who you may need to test in alpha with

   {{ actionLink({
