### Beta and live

- demonstrate how you’ve done user research with people who have access needs from the time you started designing the service
- demonstrate how you’ve tested with users who need assisted digital support
- do not assume you can solely rely on external accessibility audits, for example Digital Accessibility Centre audits (DAC)

